{"tid":270200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新居自行安裝美的冷氣 業主當場遭炸死","createTime":"2017-06-04T07:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T04:41:46.000Z","uid":72009,"like":75,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f558210db756009a04412412138d3476f3742ae","tid":270200,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:26:12.000Z","msg":"這款冷氣，香港都有售！江蘇鹽城的怡和園一名陶姓業主（49歲），昨早10時許自行在新居安裝美的（Midea）冷氣，沒料到冷氣機突然爆炸，陶男當場被炸死。知情人士透露，陶男是安裝技工，懂得安裝冷氣。目前，事故原因有待警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n保安稱，當時聽到「轟」一聲巨響，開始以為有東西掉了下來，後來才有居民稱有人安裝冷氣時發生爆炸。他到16號樓1307號單位察看，看到客廳的冷氣被炸得四分五裂，巨大的爆炸衝擊力已經將該男戶主炸到廚房的牆壁處，其面部被炸得面目全非，廚房的牆壁上到處都是血迹，該男子已沒有生命跡象。當時該男子的妻子也在家中，已經被嚇得癱坐在地。<br />\n<br />\n屋苑16號樓的外牆上，部分窗戶玻璃被炸至脫落。居民透露，陶男是拆遷戶，安排在1307和1308的雙連單位居住，家裏的裝修基本完成，已購買電器進行安裝，而陶男本身為安裝技工，沒想到會發生這樣的事情。<br />\n<br />\n警方透露，出事的冷氣機為美的牌，至於爆炸原因有待調查。為甚麼冷氣機會突然爆炸呢？廣東美的冷氣一名孫姓售後服務人員表示，初步了解，該戶人家前兩天不知道從甚麼渠道購買冷氣機，可能是用戶自己安裝時操作不當引起事故。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170604/large/1496545178_2989.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170604%2Flarge%2F1496545178_2989.jpg&h=b49baa39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170604&amp;guid=56781099&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170604%26guid%3D56781099%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=ibnFyzvvQ5u13S7MONt%2FvEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f0f21269\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170604%26guid%3D56781099%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=b798cd0d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170604&amp;guid=56781099&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c3494068f41b07d48c926860521614e6ff44fd","tid":270200,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:27:26.000Z","msg":"無電點解爆"},{"pid":"8f180b145285d6b2033932b42d7ab06cb9ff215f","tid":270200,"uid":15880,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/152818_f2fefa65deea4e402602731c7a9b502c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F152818_f2fefa65deea4e402602731c7a9b502c.jpg&h=985e47b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55bd6f8823aad205736372f57d36585ac33eff45","tid":270200,"uid":41543,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:29:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無電點解爆</blockquote><br />\n有無電同爆唔爆兩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f88d8841b1e1279f879947fc241c87d0985701","tid":270200,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97838a6b78e8f3fcb865955818687abbd23caa4","tid":270200,"uid":31060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無電點解爆</blockquote><br />\n西瓜同凳都可以爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b928a1df0c6b5fb67d3f3f66b44b591fd3f295","tid":270200,"uid":46277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:30:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/152818_f2fefa65deea4e402602731c7a9b502c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F152818_f2fefa65deea4e402602731